Convention: 
ifdh_art v1_4_0 built with art v1_08_10 and gcc v4_8_1
ifdh_art v1_4_0a built with art v1_09_02 and gcc v4_8_2

Building ifdh_art

When building for art v1_09_02, QUAL is e5
When building for art v1_08_10, QUAL is e4

ifdh_art/ups/product_deps will need to be edited to have either e4 or e5 throughout

make sure that ups is setup
mkdir working_dir
cd working_dir
source /your/source/ifdh_art/ups/setup_for_development -d QUAL
env CC=gcc CXX=g++ FC=gfortran cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/your/local/product_directory -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=$CETPKG_TYPE $CETPKG_SOURCE
make [-jN]  
make install (optional)
make package (optional)

Make package creates a distributable tarball.

